<br>
I am looking for descriptions on how the spells/songs work.  Whom to assist and how to.  What mobs to take first and when.  All those things that are considered no no's and essentials at the higher levels.<br>
<br>
My Guild is pretty young, with a fair number of low level and first time players in them.  While I have some experience with this, and am asking other sources (like talking to our enchanters), I wouldn't mind having some expert advice.<br>
<br>
What I am looking for is not so much oriented towards the CCer, but towards all the other party members.<br>
<br>
Thank you all for your help.<br>
<br>
