<br>
<br>
ASSIST THE MAIN TANK<br>
<br>
ignore all other MoBs, everybody should ONLY assist the maintank (there are tactics using several tanks for offtaunitng but forget about that for now).<br>
<br>
The main assist provides a target for anybody else and he himself gets his target from the CHANTER.<br>
<br>
I cant tell you how often it happens that I work up a mezz-line with 4 or 5 MoBs and the maintank goes in and breaks it apart, as soon as I have control I make sure I know exactly which mezz will drop next, thats very important when you get an add while your first mezz is at 30 seconds mezz time already. When the main assist target is dead I want the maintank to break mezz on the MoB with LESS seconds on its mezz but noooooo, most go for casters or better drop MoBs. WTF, these are mezzed damnit, they all have the same danger level = ZERO. We are talking about a danger and a mana waste here. When I have 2 MoBs mezzed, one with 12 secsonds left on its timer, the other with 70 seconds left I want you to take the one with 12 seconds not the other so you better hear at me. <br>
<br>
When I work with 4 to 5 MoBs my mana gets kinda low, add that I usually have to root before breaks and you have me on constant casting without much time for medding in between. YOU BETTER DONT WASTE MY MANA just because you are unable to follow a simple "get %t next please" command.<br>
<br>
<br>
So raid/group gets their target from Main assist<br>
Main assist gets his target from chanter<br>
<br>
<br>
Sharph <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmfrm17.showPrevMessage?topicID=16.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmfrm17.showNextMessage?topicID=16.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmfrm17.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=16.topic&index=5><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/addReply1.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmfrm17.threadControl?topicID=16.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/deleteThreadFire.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmfrm17.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=16.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmfrm17.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=16.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub136.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="eqenchantersrealmfrm11">General<option value="eqenchantersrealmadminnotices">Admin Notices<option value="eqenchantersrealmfrm12">Equipment<option value="eqenchantersrealmspells">Spells<option value="eqenchantersrealmfaqs">FAQs<option value="eqenchantersrealmstories">Stories<option value="eqenchantersrealmfrm7">Quests<option value="eqenchantersrealmfrm9">Tradeskills<option value="eqenchantersrealmfrm13">Auctions<option value="eqenchantersrealmfrm14">Weapons & Armor